Angelica Bridges https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angelica_Bridges 0 Angelica Bridges (born November 20, 1970) is an American actress, model, singer and dog-sitter. She was given a pictorial spread in Playboy magazine's November 2001 issue and featured as the issue's cover model. In 2017, she competed on the first season of FOX's reality game show Kicking Screaming with her survivalist partner Hakim Isler.
